title: Luck
subTitle: Moussa, a mafia leader, gives a bunch of people an opportunity to earn a hefty amount by making them participate in a game of survival.

title: Shakalaka Boom Boom
subTitle: Reggie, an aspiring singer, faces fierce opposition from an established musician determined to sabotage his career out of personal revenge.

title: Officer Arjun Singh IPS
subTitle: Arjun Pratap Singh, an IPS officer, strives to overcome multiple challenges and embarks on a mission to restore peace in society.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Ek Hi Raasta
subTitle: Army officer Vikram works with terrorist Kubla and steals vital army information for him. In the process, he ends up killing a colleague and pins the blame on a fellow soldier.

title: Dulaara

subTitle: Two brothers struggle to keep their family together as external forces like the younger brother's father-in-law try to break them apart.

subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: Phullu
subTitle: Phullu's mother decides to marry him off to make him more mature. Things take an unexpected turn when he learns about menstruation after marriage.

title: Bumper Draw
subTitle: Two men form a friendship in the most unlikely situation. Later, when they meet a rich man, they begin to devise a plan that will put an end to their financial difficulties.

subTitle: Navendu looks after his stepmother and half-brothers to fulfil the promise he has made to his father. However, their family falls apart after one of them marries a rich, controlling woman.

title: Joroo Ka Ghulam
subTitle: When Kalpana's parents believe her lies about her husband Rajesh's newfound success and decide to visit her after she delivers a baby, Kalpana finds herself in a predicament.

subTitle: Shyam, a middle-class man, falls in love with a millionaire's daughter and marries her. However, as their relationship starts deteriorating, Shyam finds solace in the company of Radha.

title: Amrit
subTitle: A widowed man and woman face abuse from their respective children and seek comfort from each other instead.

title: Avtaar

title: Jab Pyaar Kisise Hota Hai
subTitle: Sooraj Dhanrajgir, a playboy, falls in love with Komal, who rejects him because of his vices and gives him time to change. Things go awry when a little boy shows up claiming to be his son.

title: Roti
subTitle: Mangal Singh escapes prison and begins a new life, unknowingly befriending his victim's family. As he seeks redemption, his past catches up, compelling him to confront his previous misdeeds.
